OL,3,CKlopp: Mo Salah one of Liverpool's
OL,4,Cgreats
OL,6,FFormer Liverpool FC manager Jurgen
OL,7,FKlopp has paid glowing tribute to
OL,8,FMohamed Salah, describing the forward
OL,9,Fas one of the team's greatest-ever
OL,10,Fplayers and a "fantastic ambassador
OL,11,Ffor his country."
OL,13,FSalah announced he will leave
OL,14,FLiverpool at the end of the season,
OL,15,Fbringing a glittering chapter to a
OL,16,Fclose.
OL,18,FThe Egyptian star has scored 255 goals
OL,19,Fin 435 appearances, making him the
OL,20,Fthird-highest scorer in the club's
OL,21,Fhistory behind Ian Rush and Roger Hunt.
OL,26,@rD@OOUsD@QO]
