OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774789868
OL,3,CKlopp: Mo Salah one of Liverpool's
OL,4,Cgreats
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of Saturday's charity
OL,7,Fgame at Anfield, where Liverpool
OL,8,FLegends will take on Borussia Dortmund
OL,9,FLegends, Klopp was full of praise for
OL,10,FSalah.
OL,12,F"He's right up there," he said
OL,14,F"In my time, and since I'm really
OL,15,Ffollowing or working for Liverpool,
OL,16,Fhe's definitely up there with the
OL,17,Fgreatest. The numbers speak for
OL,18,Fthemselves."
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
