OL,3,CKlopp: Mo Salah one of Liverpool's
OL,4,Cgreats
OL,6,FKlopp, who signed Salah from Roma in
OL,7,F2017, highlighted the striker's impact
OL,8,Fboth on and off the pitch.
OL,10,FHe added: "He is a fantastic
OL,11,Fambassador for his country, for the
OL,12,Fwhole region there. A great guy, a
OL,13,Freal competitor.
OL,15,F"We both had our moments together, but
OL,16,Fwe always came together again quickly
OL,17,Fbecause we wanted the same thing,
OL,18,Fmaximum success for our team."
OL,26,@rD@KOUzD@^O]
