OL,3,CKlopp: Mo Salah one of Liverpool's
OL,4,Cgreats
OL,6,FDuring his time at Anfield, Salah has
OL,7,Fhelped Liverpool lift two Premier
OL,8,FLeague titles, the Champions League,
OL,9,Fan FA Cup, and two Carabao Cups.
OL,11,FHe is determined to finish his
OL,12,FLiverpool career on a high, with Arne
OL,13,FSlot's side still competing in the FA
OL,14,FCup and the Champions League.
OL,16,FThe Reds will face Manchester City in
OL,17,Fthe FA Cup quarter-finals and holders
OL,18,FParis Saint-Germain in the Champions
OL,19,FLeague last eight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
