PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774789868
OL,3,CKlopp: Mo Salah one of Liverpool's
OL,4,Cgreats
OL,6,FKlopp, who left Liverpool in summer
OL,7,F2024 after nine years at the helm,
OL,8,Freflected on the legacy Salah leaves.
OL,10,F"One of the greatest LFC players ever
OL,11,Fwill go this summer," Klopp added.
OL,13,F"Others did before, really good ones.
OL,14,FLife goes on, and that's how it should
OL,15,Fbe. I really loved being part of his
OL,16,Fcareer and his journey and hope
OL,17,Feveryone goes with this positive
OL,18,Ffeeling in this last period of the
OL,19,Fseason that everything is still
OL,20,Fpossible."
OL,26,@rD@AOU|D@JO]
