OL,3,CKlopp: Mo Salah one of Liverpool's
OL,4,Cgreats
OL,6,FReturning to Liverpool as honorary
OL,7,Fambassador for the LFC Foundation,
OL,8,FKlopp will take his place in the
OL,9,Fdugout for Saturday's sold-out charity
OL,10,Fmatch.
OL,12,FHe will be joined by club legends
OL,13,Fincluding Sir Kenny Dalglish, Ian
OL,14,FRush, John Aldridge, Steven Gerrard,
OL,15,Fand others, to raise funds for the LFC
OL,16,FFoundation and Forever Reds, the
OL,17,Fclub's former players association.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
