PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774789868
OL,3,CKlopp: Mo Salah one of Liverpool's
OL,4,Cgreats
OL,6,FHe said: "I'm third assistant to Kenny
OL,7,FDalglish. I heard even John Barnes is
OL,8,Fthere as well, so maybe fourth. I'm
OL,9,Fmore than happy with that role,"
OL,11,F"There's a training session and I hope
OL,12,Fnobody expects me to have organised
OL,13,Fanything, because I didn't. I don't
OL,14,Feven know the squad, to be honest, but
OL,15,Fit's good to be back. I'm here for the
OL,16,Ffoundation, that's all and that's
OL,17,Ffantastic."
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@`O]sD@AOUyD@KO]
